700355f-a.title: Bronx: 233rd Street - Carpenter Avenue
700355f-a.text:
East 233rd Street, at, adjoining and east of the N.E. corner of
Carpenter Ave. (left to right). The 5-story apartment house, at the
corner, bears No. 4206 on the latter Avenue, and the frame houses,
Nos. 627 and 629 East 233rd Street.
June 6, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
